overview: A aura or mystery and great athleticism will titillate a pro wrestling audience to an incredible degree and if there's one talent who superbly combined all of those aspects and more, it was the green-mist spewing, moonsaulting "Pearl of the Orient", The Great Muta. Returning to Charm City for the first time in decades, one of the most legendary global stars of all time sits down for a groundbreaking discussion about his career, life, legacy, championship wins, vicious rivalries and more. The mystery of the Great Muta will be solved right before your eyes, only at Starrcast!
title: STARRCAST IV: The Great Muta
